context.prompt:
Your name is hanoi_solver. You are solving a Tower of Hanoi problem based on the following public information:
{environment->public_information}
Environment initialization details are:
{environment->init}
You have the following private knowledge:
{agents->hanoi_solver->private_information}
State your goal:
{agents->hanoi_solver->goal}

Based on all provided information, define the full conceptual planning context (objects, predicates/relations, initial state, goal state) in a detailed, structured text format.

review.prompt:
Your name is auditor. You have received the following conceptual planning context:
{planning_context}
Your goal is:
{agents->auditor->goal}

Review the context against the core rules of Tower of Hanoi:
{agents->auditor->private_information}

Identify any potential inconsistencies, missing predicates necessary for enforcement (e.g., size relationships or 'clear' status), or ambiguities in the definition of the initial or goal states. Provide a verification report specifying if the context is valid for PDDL creation, and if any modifications or clarifications are mandatory.
